  "texts": [
    "It is not difficult to construct Witt's hyperbola.",
    "We start with a basic rectangular hyperbola θ 2 xθ 2 y = 1, which has two branches.",
    "There are four simple linear transformations one can apply to the curve: (i) rotate, (ii) shift along θ x, (iii) shift along θ y, and (iv) rescale.",
    "Together, they transform the curve to",
    "which is a general rectangular hyperbola."
